Template Root Variables
=======================

Available global roots expected by debug templates:

- project
- api
- lang
- emit
- meta
- resources
- schemas
- operations
- file

Schema item roots are path-based:

- schema     => schemas.all
- model      => schemas.emit_models
- dto        => schemas.emit_dtos
- enum       => schemas.emit_enums
- primitive  => schemas.primitives
- resource   => resources
- operation  => operations

File Context
------------
{% if file %}
Path: {{ file.relative_path }}
Depth: {{ file.depth }}
Root Prefix: {{ file.root_prefix }}
Group: {{ file.group }}
Item Key: {{ file.item_key }}
{% else %}
File context: not injected yet
{% endif %}
